        	<h2>About WonderOps</h2>
             <div class="why-cho_inner_subtext"><img src="./images/hat-wand.jpg">

WonderOps services are focused on providing value added information security services to our core product offerings of sofware development and cloud server management. The company is rooted with 25 years of Information Security and Infrastructure Management experience. The WonderOps organization believes as companies transition services to the cloud, the inherent requirement to modify how they do business must also evolve. Cloud computing adoption will be a key competitive advantage for companies who position themselves intelligently and with agility. WonderOps is a DevOps organization founded to extend all of the advantages offered by the cloud in a service model that minimizes the barriers and complexities of a company to securely transition business operations to the cloud. Consistent with our company mantra, we perform the IT magic, leaving you the freedom to grow your business. 
